role 'Finance Viewer'
	modelPermission: read
	description: Read-only access to the Finance Reporting model for finance team members and business stakeholders. No row-level restrictions — all entities, departments, accounts, and periods are visible. For entity-restricted access, create an Entity Analyst role with a DimEntity[IsConsolidated] = TRUE filter or an entity-specific filter using USERPRINCIPALNAME() and a user-entity mapping table.
